data.name: Parent World Name
data.description: The name of the worldzone that this map belongs to.

data.name: Grid Length
data.description: The length of the stage, in whatever arbitrary units that are also used by other map files. Usually the same as grid Width.

data.name: Grid Width
data.description: The width of the stage, in whatever arbitrary units that are also used by other map files. Usuall the same as grid Length.
